-- U.S.’s Treasury’s Miller Says Economy Showing Stable Growth
-- B y   K a s i a   K l i m a s i n s k a
-- 2013-06-25T13:41:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-25/u-s-s-treasury-s-miller-says-economy-showing-stable-growth.html
The U.S. economy is showing signs of
stable growth and officials need to focus next on ensuring the
 federal budget  deficit keeps narrowing, said Mary Miller, the
U.S. Treasury Department’s undersecretary for domestic finance.  “Now it’s time to start bringing those deficits down,”
she said at a conference today in Philadelphia.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kasia Klimasinska in Washington at 
